<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Welcome to Tool Box Gamez</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f7;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .email-wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 40px 0;
        }

        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .logo {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0 0 0;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .logo img {
            max-height: 60px;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #FFAA01;
            color: #000000;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        .body {
            padding: 30px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .body h2 {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        .info-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .info-table td {
            padding: 8px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .info-table td:first-child {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #555;
            width: 140px;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999;
            padding: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-container">
            <div class="logo">
                <img src="" alt="Tool Box Gamez Logo" />
            </div>
            <div class="header">
                <h1>Welcome to Tool Box Gamez</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="body">
                <h2>Hi <%= employee %>,</h2>
                <p>Welcome to <strong>Tool Box Gamez</strong>! We’re thrilled to have you onboard. 🕹️</p>
                <p>You’ve been added to our platform by <strong>
                        <%= manager %>
                    </strong>. Below are your login credentials and account details:</p>

                <table class="info-table">
                    <tr>
                        <td>Email:</td>
                        <td>
                            <%= email %>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Password:</td>
                        <td>
                            <%= password %>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Designation:</td>
                        <td>
                            <%= designation %>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Department:</td>
                        <td>
                            <%= department %>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>

                <p>Please keep this information safe and secure.</p>
                <p>If you have any questions or need help getting started, don’t hesitate to reach out.</p>

                <p>Game on!<br>The Tool Box Gamez Team</p>
            </div>
            <div class="footer">
                &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Tool Box Gamez. All rights reserved.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>